data.description: Welcome to ''The Hickory'' located at 109 Donovan Lane in the Stables! Built by the custom Dave Hobba Builders, this home is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch which holds an additional room for an office! The living room, dining room and kitchen have a continuous, approachable flow with white Shaker, soft close cabinets, granite countertops, LVP & classic light fixtures throughout. The primary suite is placed privately toward the back of the home with all of the amenities including a large walk in closet and beautiful shower. With a generous mudroom and laundry, it's easy access to the 2 car garage. Conveniently located near I75, eateries and shopping, this home offers a warm entry and a large back porch just waiting for you! Please schedule your private showing today!
